=== FINAL SUMMARY ===
Math correct: YES (semicircle benchmark verified to 0.64% accuracy).
Best LB obtained: NULL (none derivable from this direction).
vs 1.2802: BELOW (min free max ~ 1.22 -- so even reverse-direction LB doesn't help).
Promising: NO. Direction is dead.

Key reasons:
1. supp(mu boxed_plus mu) can EXCEED [-1/2, 1/2] (broken support correspondence)
2. ||free||_inf vs ||classical||_inf has no consistent ordering: ratio in [0.53, 1.05] across random configs
3. min ||free||_inf ~ 1.22 < 1.28: no useful LB transfer
4. Log-log scaling: free_max ~ classical_max^0.52 (incompatible scaling)
5. Pearson correlation only 0.62

Verdict: Free probability gives a structurally different convolution that does
not bound classical convolution from either direction usefully.

Total time: ~3 minutes wall clock.
